Died
384 AD (traditionally)
Maastricht


Venerated in
Roman Catholic Church
Eastern Orthodox Church[1]


Major shrine
Basilica of Saint Servatius, Maastricht


Feast
13 May


Attributes
So-called "Key of Saint Servatius", crozier, dragon (under his feet)


Patronage
