2 Legend
3 Legacy

3.1 In Maastricht
3.2 Elsewhere


4 See also
5 Notes
6 Sources and references
7 External links



History[edit]




Tomb of Saint Servatius (behind the back wall) inside Basilica of Saint Servatius, Maastricht


